### âœ… **PART 5: Task CRUD API**

### ðŸŽ¯ Objectives:

- Create `Task` model with fields:
    - title, description, status, dueDate, createdBy
- Create routes:
    
    ```bash
    POST /api/tasks
    GET /api/tasks
    GET /api/tasks/:id
    PUT /api/tasks/:id
    DELETE /api/tasks/:id
    
    ```
    
- Only allow user to access their own tasks

